data.description: Welcome to this recently remodeled, beautiful Williamsburg home.  This home boasts 3 bedrooms, 1 and 1 half bathrooms. A gorgeous open kitchen with island and second floor laundry for convenience. Bring your belongings and be at home for the holidays.  Sale is contingent on seller securing alternate housing.
